items.title: Project Tracker
items.caption: To-do list and project tracker.
items.description: I created this as a personal to-do list app. It evolves over time, but the basic idea is to keep track of the various projects I am working on and maintain and prioritize a to-do list, linking tasks to projects.

items.title: Daily Planner
items.caption: Daily planner with weather forecasts.
items.description: I made this because I wanted to connect my projects to a calendar, and I wanted to visualize it as a list with weather forecasts retrieved via API and color-coded so that I can see the weather for the next week.

items.title: World Explorer
items.summary: Drive around the globe, watch out for aliens.
items.caption: Drive around the globe, watch out for aliens.
items.description: AKA World Invasion. This is a work in progress that combines several game design elements. The user drives a car around a map of the world, discovering landmarks powered by Wikidata, taking on a fleet of flying saucers along the way.

links.label: Play the Game
links.note: (desktop only, doesn't work yet on mobile)

items.title: Live Events Finder
items.caption: Find live events near you.
items.description: This is a proof-of-concept live event finder built on the Ticketmaster API.

items.title: Portfolio
items.caption: Showcase projects.
items.description: This is the portfolio website that I created for this portfolio. Working on it from time to time. Available in GitHub.

items.title: Places Catalog
items.summary: Keep track of places around the world.
items.caption: Keep track of places around the world.
items.description: I developed this to keep track of notable places I want to visit, have visited, etc.

items.title: UMLS Metathesaurus Browser
items.caption: Search biomedical terminologies.
items.description: I developed this website to provide access to NLM terminology products and browse the Unified Medical Language System, a collection of concepts from biomedical terminologies. Requires a free account in order to browse and search.

items.title: UMLS API Interactive Interface
items.summary: Learn to use the UMLS API.
items.caption: Learn to use the UMLS API.
items.description: I built this interactive interface that illustrates the functionality of the UMLS API.

items.title: UMLS Similarity Engine
items.caption: Vector search for biomedical concepts.
items.description: This is an exploration of biomedical similarity search. The idea was to see if I could use an existing model trained on the UMLS to set up a search of UMLS concepts. Input a string and return UMLS concepts that have vector similarity based on deep learning. Training was time-intensive, so I didn't get very far, but I did end up with a working search interface and API. Explore on GitHub.
